            "y1": 2051,
            "x2": 2045,
            "y2": 2181
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 17,
        "text": "ब्रह्मसों उपजो ब्रह्महि जानौ । यामें संशय कछू न मानौ ५१",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jnanadasa1895_12_textline_17.png",
