            "x1": 271,
            "y1": 2181,
            "x2": 2036,
            "y2": 2302
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 18,
        "text": "जीवात्मा परमातम माहीं । थोरो भेद करत जो आहीं ।। सो मू-",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jnanadasa1895_12_textline_18.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 265,
            "y1": 2299,
            "x2": 2048,
            "y2": 2422
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 19,
        "text": "ढ़ात्मा निश्चय जानौ । जन्म मरण भयताहि पिछानौ ५२ जा",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jnanadasa1895_12_textline_19.png",
        "bounding_box": {
